{"tid":2229344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"截斷東澳古道 遊人掃興折返","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T10:17:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa191ad14c87dabe2e46916f2aa77241a4382843","tid":2229344,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/MGVNYB5PHZEEBATX3UG6SVA6JY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FMGVNYB5PHZEEBATX3UG6SVA6JY%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=2c099e02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FMGVNYB5PHZEEBATX3UG6SVA6JY%2F&h=e0820d66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/MGVNYB5PHZEEBATX3UG6SVA6JY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n截斷東澳古道 遊人掃興折返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SU_rXPlfiHVi1Bqq8Ac6UsYiS1E=/2205x1240/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EXGOMS7XPRF7XNS7UNV2F6UCGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSU_rXPlfiHVi1Bqq8Ac6UsYiS1E%3D%2F2205x1240%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEXGOMS7XPRF7XNS7UNV2F6UCGY.jpg&h=a3aa6efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■東澳古道屬中長線行山路徑，是行山熱門地方。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙螺灣村近日封村，攔腰中斷東澳古道由東涌至大澳的郊遊遠足路線，令行山人士怨聲載道，行山人士因被迫中途折返大感掃興，更有市民鬧爆村民把山徑路段當私人路段圍封，做法自私。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沿路無告示 獲市民提醒<br />\n<br />\n連續四天假期，到東澳古道行山郊遊的市民絡繹不絕，但他們在途中才知道路線因為沙螺灣村鎖上鐵閘而中斷，需原路折返，感到極為掃興。<br />\n<br />\n昨日張先生一行12人到古道郊遊，「本身諗住去大澳，途中先知去唔到」，他指沿路均未見村民擺放告示，通知他人前路不通，但就有其他行山市民善意提醒。<br />\n<br />\n張先生不滿表示，「私家路可以封，但如果唔係私家路，係公家路就唔封得啦！」最。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了沙螺灣村，記者曾到附近的䃟頭村，發現雖然䃟頭村村民展示「私人地段」橫額，但未有任何封路措施，只提醒行山人士做好防疫措施，入村時戴上口罩。"}]}